bile revenue is embedded within the Enterprise & Government sub-segment of the Connectivity segment. The filing states:\n\n- In 2025, **consumer subscribers represented over 60%** of Connectivity segment revenue\n- Starlink Mobile is expected to become a **"significant new contributor"** of Connectivity segment growth\n\nThere is no disclosure of the exact revenue Starlink Mobile generated, nor its percentage of Connectivity segment revenue.\n\n---\n\n## Market Sizing Context\n\nThe filing does provide a top-down market estimate: using region-specific ARPU assumptions (weighted average of **$8/month per user** globally), and the total number of connected devices globally, SpaceX estimates the **Starlink Mobile market opportunity at $740 billion**.',
